Package Maps

Contains maps of different locations

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArielMap
    A game map of Ariel University, (Enum value: MapType.ArielUniversity)
    Map
    an abstract Map class which defines the basic properties of map such as image, current screen range, Geodetic Map range, and original screen range.
    MapFactory
    Map Factory! you can generate/get maps with this class! using the FlyWeight design pattern to store already created instances of maps..
    MapRange
    Stores the polar/geodetic map range coordinates, have different mathods of Width and Height.
    TelAvivMap
    A game map of Tel-Aviv city, (Enum value: MapType.TelAviv)
    testMap
    a JUNIT4 class for testing functionality of Map class.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MapFactory.MapType
    Enums of different maps.
